npx npm-cli-login -u {username} -p {password} -e {email} -r https://sencha.myget.org/F/{feed}/npm/ -s @sencha —quotes
- The following message will appear in the termanal/command window after successful login

<div class="border">http 201 https://sencha.myget.org/F/{feed}/npm/-/user/org.couchdb.user:{username}</div>

